des:
Learn more about the 2022 Hyundai TUCSON!

Hyundai Driver provides in-depth information on the multitude of amazing features in the new 2022 Hyundai Tucson.

After enabling, say "Alexa, open hyundai driver" to begin.

Once in the skill, you can ask for info on each feature (for example, "infotainment screen").
